### Get all student help requests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/requests

### Filter by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/requests?status=OPEN

### Filter by category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/requests?category=ACADEMICS

### Create a help request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentName": "Rahul",
  "title": "Need help in Spring Boot basics",
  "description": "I have an interview soon and need a simple explanation of Controller, Service and Repository.",
  "category": "ACADEMICS",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

### Update status
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/requests/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "RESOLVED"
}

### Add comment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/requests/1/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "authorName": "Ankit",
  "message": "I have uploaded my DBMS notes. Check the drive link in the class group."
}

### Get comments
GET http://localhost:8080/api/requests/1/comments

### Delete request
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/requests/3
